summary: This cable discusses several topics, including Juan Manuel Fernandez's desire to leave Cuba, a request to take Luis Rodriguez into the Jaguar Group, authorization to instruct A-35, information about an assassination attempt against Fidel Castro, the movement of tracked tanks, a Russian ship delivering fertilizer, and the defection of Commandant 'Contreras' and others.
title: 2025 RELEASE UNDER THE PRESIDENT JOHN F. KENNEDY ASSASSINATION RECORDS ACT OF 1992
